<doc id="292823" wikidata="Q8015430" url="?curid=292823" title="William McGuigan">
<text>Dr. William J. McGuigan (July 18, 1853 – December 25, 1908) was the tenth Mayor of Vancouver, British Columbia and served one term in 1904. He was born in Stratford, Canada West and was buried in Mountain View Cemetery in Vancouver.

